---
const mockupSrc = '/images/mockups/product-screen.png';
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-16 bg-[#F6F8F7]">
  <div class="max-w-[1160px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="section-eyebrow mb-3">画面イメージ</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">直感的に使えるダッシュボード</h2>
      <p class="text-[#4B5563] mt-4 text-sm md:text-base">採点・集計・分析まで、シンプルな画面で管理できます。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <img
        src={mockupSrc}
        alt="澄の画面イメージ"
        class="block w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-[#E5E7EB] bg-white object-contain"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
